About Legacy Cigar Bar & Lounge
Legacy Cigar Bar & Lounge brings together the best of both worlds with our wine, craft beers, and premium cigars, all with a positive and welcoming atmosphere. Our lively ambiance invites good spirits and good times, where you and your family and friends can enjoy playing, singing, and more. With quality service from our staff, you will not find a better place around, so come check us out at Legacy Cigar Bar & Lounge!
